<h1>Minecraft Art</h1>
<br>
<h3>Retro Re:Imagine Part 1</h3>
<br>
<br>
<p>Part 1 of Retro Re:Imagined</p>
<br>
<p>The beginning of this project was to make art using Minecraft.I first decided to create a sculpture of a 3d 8-bit Mario. Later down the line I expanded on this idea further by 
making a sculpture of a 3d 8-bit Sonic and a 3d 8-bit Link to garner the theme of old video games reintroduced in 3d art.
</p>
<br>
