<p>The cultural significance of my piece is that Mario, Link, and Sonic are video game icons. Everyone has played a Mario 
game before and Mario is arguably the first video game character that made video games popular in the first place.
Mario's presence in video games helped inspire other creators to create games based on his influence. 
These video game characters are what developed video game culture and I wanted to celebrate that history by making it part of my art.
</p>

